/*
 * OpenMP 6.0 clauses with the unique property. The replayable clause is
 * included as corrected by the November 2025 OpenMP 6.0 errata.
 *
 * This is clause cardinality only. Modifier/category-specific cardinality,
 * clause sets, and directive-specific restrictions are validated separately.
 */

